# bball-cli

Command-line interface for the bball ecosystem.

## Installation

```bash
pip install bball-cli
```

Or as part of the bball ecosystem:
```bash
pip install bball[cli]
```

## Usage

```bash
bball info  # Show installed components
bball version  # Show version information
```
